# Codex Tasks: Benchmark Source Adapters

These tasks make benchmark packs come from real-world sources, not only Aim Brain-specific files.

---

## Task BSA-001: Add BenchmarkSourceAdapter Types

Create:

```text
src/engine/benchmarks/sources/BenchmarkSourceAdapter.ts
```

Include:
- BenchmarkSourceType
- BenchmarkSourceInput
- BenchmarkSourceMetadata
- BenchmarkSourceImportResult
- BenchmarkSourceImportError
- BenchmarkSourceAdapter

Acceptance:
- Types compile.
- No UI dependency.
- No benchmark-specific logic in shared source types.

---

## Task BSA-002: Add Local JSON Source Adapter

Create:

```text
src/engine/benchmarks/sources/localJsonAdapter.ts
```

Acceptance:
- reads local pack.json
- parses JSON
- validates BenchmarkPack
- returns clear errors for invalid JSON
- returns source metadata

---

## Task BSA-003: Add Built-In Pack Source Adapter

Create:

```text
src/engine/benchmarks/sources/builtInPackAdapter.ts
```

Acceptance:
- loads bundled pack JSON files
- validates them on startup/test
- failed built-in pack validation fails tests

---

## Task BSA-004: Add Generic CSV Adapter

Create:

```text
src/engine/benchmarks/sources/localCsvAdapter.ts
```

Acceptance:
- imports a simple known CSV shape
- maps rows into scenarios/ranks/thresholds
- supports progress-only scenarios
- returns warnings for missing optional data

