## Task BSA-005: Add Source Import Preview

Create a UI-neutral preview model:

```text
src/engine/benchmarks/sources/createBenchmarkImportPreview.ts
```

Preview should include:
- benchmark name
- source type
- version
- scenario count
- rank count
- threshold count
- supported platforms
- warnings
- errors
- official/community/custom status

---

## Task BSA-006: Add Source Install Flow

Connect source adapters to existing pack installer.

Flow:

```text
source input
↓
adapter import
↓
validation
↓
preview
↓
confirm install
↓
copy/store pack
↓
registry update
```

Acceptance:
- install local JSON pack
- invalid pack blocked
- warnings shown but can be confirmed
- source metadata stored

